ADD colony.2001.name:0 "Trouble in Paradise"
CN2 colony.2001.name:0 "天堂的烦恼"
ADD colony.2001.desc:0 "Local political drama on [Root.GetName] has resulted in increased support among a small group of rebels, opposed to our underlying ethics. Their increased support have enabled them to gain more power in the region and vote for their own causes with limited success."
CN2 colony.2001.desc:0 " [Root.GetName] 本地的政府失误导致一小群叛军收获了更多支持者，他们反对我们传统的种群思潮。支持他们的人越来越多，这让他们在该区域获得了更大的权利。这样的支持同时也让他们在获得民众支持上取得了一定成功，他们可以利用这些支持来发展自己的事业。"
ADD colony.2001.a:0 "We stand divided."
CN2 colony.2001.a:0 "和他们划清界限。"
ADD colony.2001.a.military.tooltip:1 "§B3 £pops£ Pops§! on [Root.GetName] converts one step closer to §YMilitarism§!."
CN2 colony.2001.a.military.tooltip:1 " [Root.GetName] 上的§B3个£pops人口§!向§Y军国主义§!进一步转变。"
