ADD colony.2005.name:0 "From Beneath the Waves"
CN2 colony.2005.name:0 "波涛之下"
ADD colony.2005.desc:0 "The colonizers on [Root.GetName] regularly explore the planet in hopes of finding more resources to help with day-to-day life. A recent expedition to the north pole has now unveiled a large object on the bottom of the ocean: An alien battle cruiser.\n\nThe pressure of the deep will prove a challenge, but it is possible to get to the ship."
CN2 colony.2005.desc:0 "为了改善日常生活， [Root.GetName] 的殖民者开始定期探索星球上的资源。最近一次北极探索时，在深海发现了一个巨大物体：一艘外星战斗巡洋舰。\n\n深海的压强可能会造成困难，但仍有可能打捞这艘沉船。"
ADD colony.2005.a:0 "Try and salvage it."
CN2 colony.2005.a:0 "尝试打捞。"
ADD colony.2005.b:0 "Scrap it to learn its secrets."
CN2 colony.2005.b:0 "拆解并研究其中的秘密。"
ADD colony.2006.desc:0 "The salvage mission on [Root.GetName] has succeeded! The ancient cruiser that lay on the bottom of the ocean has been resurfaced and repaired. It is a wondrous sight to behold, and from repairing it our engineers have learnt some of the secrets behind its design."
CN2 colony.2006.desc:0 " [Root.GetName] 的打捞任务顺利进行！沉在海底的远古巡洋舰重新浮出水面，并已修理完毕。真是蔚为大观，通过修理它，我们的工程师学到了其设计背后的秘密。"
ADD colony.2006.a.material:0 "Our efforts pave the way forward!"
CN2 colony.2006.a.material:0 "我们的努力将引领我们向前！"
ADD colony.2006.a.phile:0 "A historic day!"
CN2 colony.2006.a.phile:0 "具有历史意义的一天！"
ADD colony.2006.a.tooltip:0 "§YYour Empire§! gains the §G$streamlined_ship_design$§! modifier.\n\nGain a §YCruiser§!-class ship."
CN2 colony.2006.a.tooltip:0 "§Y帝国§!获得§G$streamlined_ship_design$§!的修正。\n\n获得一艘§Y巡洋舰§!类型的飞船。"
ADD colony.2007.desc:0 "The attempts to salvage the giant ship that was found in [Root.GetName]'s waters have yielded some insight into the ship's design. The ship's maneuvering algorithms are easily transferable to our own hardware, enabling our fleets to become swifter and more energy efficient.\n\nUnfortunately the ship itself is beyond saving, but its hull will supply us with enough materials to make up for that."
CN2 colony.2007.desc:0 "我们尝试从 [Root.GetName] 的深海打捞这艘巨型飞船，并对其舰体设计有了一定发现。该船的机动算法很容易改用到我们的硬件上，让我们的飞船更加灵活，更加节能。\n\n可惜的是，该船本身无法抢修了，但我们仍可以从其舰体上回收一些材料。"
ADD colony.2007.a.phobe:0 "No alien ship would surpass ours anyway!"
CN2 colony.2007.a.phobe:0 "反正外星飞船是无法和我们的飞船比拟的！"
ADD colony.2007.a.phile:0 "Any gift from cosmos' children is valuable!"
CN2 colony.2007.a.phile:0 "宇宙中任何种群留下的馈赠都是有价值的！"
ADD colony.2007.a:0 "§YYour Empire§! gains the §G$streamlined_ship_design$§! modifier.\n\n"
CN2 colony.2007.a:0 "§Y帝国§!获得§G$streamlined_ship_design$§!的修正。"
ADD colony.2008.desc:0 "The explosion can be heard for miles, as the salvage operation of the submerged cruiser ends in disaster. The people of [Root.GetName] are without harm, yet parts of the settlement are destroyed.\n\nThe ship itself is far beyond repair, ripped apart by the explosion. Luckily, many of the scattered pieces of the hull can be salvaged."
CN2 colony.2008.desc:0 "爆炸声从数里之外都听得清清楚楚，打捞沉船的行动以灾难性失败告终。 [Root.GetName] 的居民没有受到伤害，但一部分建筑遭到了破坏。\n\n沉船被炸得粉碎，已经无法修理。所幸，我们回收到了许多残片。"
ADD colony.2008.a.tooltip:0 "A £building£ Building on [Root.GetName] is §Rruined§!.\n\n"
CN2 colony.2008.a.tooltip:0 " [Root.GetName] 上的一栋£building建筑被§R摧毁§!。"
ADD colony.2010.name:0 "A Change of Heart"
CN2 colony.2010.name:0 "思维转变"
ADD colony.2010.desc.spirit:0 "As we have grown our roots on [Root.GetName] certain individuals have begun to stray from our beaten path. That is to be expected, but these have supporters. The group feel our spiritualistic view of the universe is not leading us forward fast enough, assured that a more materialistic view of the cosmos is the answer."
CN2 colony.2010.desc.spirit:0 "随着我们在 [Root.GetName] 扎根落地，某些居民开始偏离我们原本的宗教事务。虽然情有可原，但他们已经拥有了不少的支持者。该社会认为，我们的唯心主义的世界观无法快速引领我们前进，只有更加唯物主义的宇宙观才是真理。"
ADD colony.2010.desc.material:0 "As our expansion on [Root.GetName] has stabilized, certain individuals have begun to move away from our view of the world. A group of spiritualists have begun to peacefully propagate against our government. They see that our materialistic view of the cosmos is limiting us and distancing us from the soul."
CN2 colony.2010.desc.material:0 "随着我们在 [Root.GetName] 上的扩张逐步稳定，某些居民开始偏离我们原本的世界观。一群唯心主义者开始渗透到我们的统治体系。该社会认为，我们的唯物主义宇宙观会限制自身的精神发展。"
ADD colony.2010.a.spirit:0 "Leave them be to find their own way."
CN2 colony.2010.a.spirit:0 "任其发展。"
ADD colony.2010.a.spirit.tooltip:2 "All §YMaterialist§!§B Pops§! on [Root.GetName] gain the §Y$opinion_respected$§! modifier with the following effects:\n£happiness£ Happiness §G+25%§! for 20 years. §Y$materialist_attraction$§! modifier added with the following effects:\n Materialist Ethics Attraction §G+100%§! for 20 years"
CN2 colony.2010.a.spirit.tooltip:2 " [Root.GetName] 上的所有§Y唯物主义§!§B人口§!获得了§Y$opinion_respected$§!的修正，效果为：\n£happiness幸福度§G+25%§!，时长20年。增加§Y$materialist_attraction$§!的修正，效果为：\n唯物主义的种群思潮吸引力§G+100%§!，时长20年"
ADD colony.2010.a.material:0 "They are no threat to our pursuits."
CN2 colony.2010.a.material:0 "他们不会对我们构成威胁。"
ADD colony.2010.a.material.tooltip:2 "All §YSpiritualist§! Pops on [Root.GetName] gain the §Y$opinion_respected$§! modifier with the following effects:\n£happiness£ Happiness §G+25%§! for 20 years.\n\n§Y$spiritualist_attraction$§! modifier added with the following effects:\nSpiritualist Ethics Attraction §G+100%§! for 20 years."
CN2 colony.2010.a.material.tooltip:2 " [Root.GetName] 上的所有§Y唯心主义§!的人口获得了§Y$opinion_respected$§!的修正，效果为：\n£happiness幸福度§G+25%§!，时长20年。\n\n增加§Y$spiritualist_attraction$§!的修正，效果为：\n唯心主义的种群思潮吸引力§G+100%§!，时长20年"
ADD colony.2010.b:0 "Bribe their leaders."
CN2 colony.2010.b:0 "贿赂他们的领袖。"
ADD colony.2010.b.tooltip:0 "No §B£pops£ Pops§! convert to a new ethic.\n\n"
CN2 colony.2010.b.tooltip:0 "没有§B£pops人口§!改变种群思潮。"
ADD colony.2010.c.material:0 "Spread propaganda to oppose them."
CN2 colony.2010.c.material:0 "展开大规模的反制公告。"
ADD colony.2010.c.material.tooltip:2 "Will attempt to dissuade §YSpiritualist§! §B£pops£ Pops§! on [Root.GetName] and promote §YMaterialism§!."
CN2 colony.2010.c.material.tooltip:2 " [Root.GetName] 上的§B3个£pops人口§!向§Y唯心主义§!进一步转变。\n\n我们努力的结果将在之后揭晓。"
ADD colony.2010.c.spirit:0 "Have spiritual guides re-direct them."
CN2 colony.2010.c.spirit:0 "让精神向导帮他们改邪归正。"
ADD colony.2010.c.spirit.tooltip:2 "Will attempt to dissuade §YMaterialist§! §B£pops£ Pops§! on [Root.GetName] and promote §YSpiritualism§!."
CN2 colony.2010.c.spirit.tooltip:2 " [Root.GetName] 上的§B3个£pops人口§!向§Y唯物主义§!进一步转变。\n\n我们努力的结果将在之后揭晓。"
ADD colony.2011.desc.base:0 "Our attempts at re-directing the parts of the population prone to oppose our core ideals have finally paid off."
CN2 colony.2011.desc.base:0 "成功对部分试图反对我们主要思潮的人口进行了重新教导。"
ADD colony.2011.desc.spirit:1 "Thanks to the tireless efforts of our spiritual leaders we have finally turned the tide, and are bringing more and more faithless into the fold. Not only materialists, but people of all persuasions have seen the light and are casting away their former beliefs. Pray they will never stray from the righteous path again."
CN2 colony.2011.desc.spirit:1 "多亏了我们的精神领袖的不懈努力，我们终于力挽狂澜，吸引来了越来越多的无信仰人士。这些人不限于唯物主义者，甚至乎包括了其他宗教人士。愿他们从此不再误入歧途。"
ADD colony.2011.desc.material:1 "$colony.2011.desc.base$ Our propaganda machine has worked as promised. Not only spiritualists, but people of all persuasions are seeing reason and casting aside their former delusions in favor of materialism."
CN2 colony.2011.desc.material:1 "$colony.2011.desc.base$我们的公告发布者顺利完成了任务，但并非一帆风顺。经过努力，这些迷失者的数量越来越少，已经不值得一提了。"
ADD colony.2011.a.spirit.tooltip:2 "§Y$spiritualist_attraction$§! modifier added with the following effects:\nSpiritualist Ethics Attraction §G+100%§! for 20 years."
CN2 colony.2011.a.spirit.tooltip:2 "增加§Y$spiritualist_attraction$§!的修正，效果为：\n唯心主义的种群思潮吸引力§G+100%§!，时长20年。"
ADD colony.2011.a.material.tooltip:2 "§Y$materialist_attraction$§! modifier added with the following effects:\nMaterialist Ethics Attraction §G+100%§! for 20 years."
CN2 colony.2011.a.material.tooltip:2 "增加§Y$materialist_attraction$§!的修正，效果为：\n唯物主义的种群思潮吸引力§G+100%§!，时长20年。"
ADD colony.2012.desc:1 "Our attempts to change the minds of our people on [Root.GetName] have backfired horribly. By banding together over our subjugation attempts they have gained even more followers, making them stronger than ever."
CN2 colony.2012.desc:1 " [Root.GetName] 上改变人们看法的计划适得其反。面对我们的镇压，他们团结一致并吸引了更多的成员，他们现在的势力更大了。在混乱中，为了展现自己的实力，他们摧毁了城区的大部分建筑。"
ADD colony.2012.a.spirit.tooltip:1 "All Materialist Pops on [Root.GetName] gain the §R$opinion_disrespected$§! modifier with the following effects:\n£happiness£ Happiness §R-40%§!\n\n§Y$materialist_attraction$§! modifier added with the following effects:\nMaterialist Ethics Attraction §G+100%§! for 20 years."
CN2 colony.2012.a.spirit.tooltip:1 " [Root.GetName] 上的所有唯物主义的人口获得了§R$opinion_disrespected$§!的修正，效果为：\n£happiness幸福度§G-40%§!，时长20年。\n\n增加§Y$materialist_attraction$§!的修正，效果为：\n唯物主义的种群思潮吸引力§G+100%§!，时长20年"
ADD colony.2012.a.material.tooltip:2 "All Spiritualist Pops on [Root.GetName] gain the §R$opinion_disrespected$§! modifier with the following effects:\n£happiness£ Happiness §R-40%§!\n\n§Y$spiritualist_attraction$§! modifier added with the following effects:\nSpiritualist Ethics Attraction §G+100%§! for 20 years."
CN2 colony.2012.a.material.tooltip:2 " [Root.GetName] 上的所有唯心主义的人口获得了§R$opinion_disrespected$§!的修正，效果为：\n£happiness幸福度§G-40%§!，时长20年。\n\n增加§Y$spiritualist_attraction$§!的修正，效果为：\n唯心主义的种群思潮吸引力§G+100%§!，时长20年"
ADD colony.2015.name:0 "An Odd Factor"
CN2 colony.2015.name:0 "古怪工厂"
ADD colony.2015.desc:0 "A group of investigators have found a hidden factory on [Root.GetName]. The building and its state of decay tells of an old civilization, one that excelled at constructing things that stood the test of time.\n\nOur population would easily be able to use the facility to add to the colony's production output."
CN2 colony.2015.desc:0 "一队调查小组在 [Root.GetName] 上发现了隐藏的工厂。根据建筑构架和磨损程度判断，它源自一个古老文明，这个文明十分擅长建造经得起时间考验的建筑。\n\n我们可以轻松使用这个工厂，增加殖民地的产出。"
ADD colony.2015.a.tooltip:0 "An §S£building£ Odd Factory§! appears on the surface of [Root.GetName]."
CN2 colony.2015.a.tooltip:0 " [Root.GetName] 的地表出现一座§S£building古怪工厂§!。"
ADD colony.2016.desc:0 "The crew we assigned to work the odd factory on [Root.GetName] has disappeared! We could send a new workforce to take their place, or we could raze the facility to the ground, making sure that this will not happen again."
CN2 colony.2016.desc:0 "在 [Root.GetName] 上古怪工厂工作的员工突然消失了！我们可以派遣工人替补，或者以防万一，直接将工厂夷为平地。"
ADD colony.2016.a:0 "It still suits our needs."
CN2 colony.2016.a:0 "这仍对我们有用。"
ADD colony.2016.a.tooltip:1 "A £pop£ §YPop§! has gone missing on [Root.GetName]."
CN2 colony.2016.a.tooltip:1 "[Root.GetName]上的一个£pop£ §Y人口§!失踪了。"
ADD colony.2016.b:0 "Demolish it."
CN2 colony.2016.b:0 "拆毁它。"
ADD colony.2016.b.tooltip:0 "The §S£building£ Odd Factory§! is destroyed."
CN2 colony.2016.b.tooltip:0 "§S£building古怪工厂§!已被摧毁。"
ADD colony.2017.desc:0 "A second group of individuals has gone missing after working at the odd factory! Fortunately one of the workers was able to leave a recording behind, revealing that there are traps capturing unsuspecting workers.\n\nThe traps have been disabled and we should be able to use the factory without further issues. However, the populace are none too happy about the potential death trap, no matter what we say."
CN2 colony.2017.desc:0 "到那个古怪工厂工作后，第二队工人也失踪了！所幸，其中一个工人留下了记录。记录显示那里有不少的陷阱，这些陷阱专门用来抓捕毫无防备的工人。\n\n陷阱已经移除，现在应该可以正常使用工厂了。但不论如何解释，民众仍对潜在的致命陷阱忧心忡忡。"
ADD colony.2017.a:0 "The people will get used to it."
CN2 colony.2017.a:0 "人们会适应的。"
ADD colony.2017.b:0 "Invest in securing the location."
CN2 colony.2017.b:0 "投资该地的安保设施。"
ADD colony.2017.a.tooltip:0 "Another Pop goes missing on [Root.GetName].\n\n"
CN2 colony.2017.a.tooltip:0 " [Root.GetName] 又失踪一个成员。"
ADD colony.2017.b.tooltip:0 "Another Pop goes missing on [Root.GetName].\n\n"
CN2 colony.2017.b.tooltip:0 " [Root.GetName] 又失踪一个成员。"
ADD colony.2018.desc:0 "The factory has exploded due to workers triggering some sort of self-destruct program. Luckily no one was hurt before the old construct fell to the ground.\n\nWe should be able to recover some of the production from the wreckage."
CN2 colony.2018.desc:0 "由于工人触发了某种自毁程序，这个工厂爆炸了。所幸建筑倒塌时没有人员伤亡。\n\n我们应该可以从残骸中回收一些资源。"
ADD colony.2018.a:0 "Recover the energy production."
CN2 colony.2018.a:0 "回收能源资源。"
ADD colony.2018.b:0 "Recover the mineral production."
CN2 colony.2018.b:0 "回收矿物资源。"
ADD colony.2018.a.tooltip:1 "The §YOdd Factory§! on [Root.GetName] is §Rruined§!.\n\nAdds the following to the surface of [Root.GetName]:\n£energy£ §G+4§!"
CN2 colony.2018.a.tooltip:1 " [Root.GetName] 上的§Y古怪工厂§!被§R摧毁§!。\n\n [Root.GetName] 的地表增加下列资源：\n£energy §G+4§!"
ADD colony.2018.b.tooltip:1 "The §YOdd Factory§! on [Root.GetName] is §Rruined§!.\n\nAdds the following to the surface of [Root.GetName]:\n£minerals£ §G+4§!"
CN2 colony.2018.b.tooltip:1 " [Root.GetName] 上的§Y古怪工厂§!被§R摧毁§!。\n\n [Root.GetName] 的地表增加下列资源：\n£minerals §G+4§!"
ADD colony.2019.desc:0 "No reports of any problems have been issued from the odd factory on [Root.GetName]. It seems like the colony will maintain the projected production estimates."
CN2 colony.2019.desc:0 " [Root.GetName] 上的古怪工厂并未出现任何异常。殖民地将维持预计的产出。"
ADD colony.2020.desc:0 "The demolition crew has briefed us that the factory on [Root.GetName] has been successfully removed. Maybe for the better.\n\nWe should be able to recover some of the production from the wreckage."
CN2 colony.2020.desc:0 "我们的拆除团队传来消息， [Root.GetName] 的工厂已被移除。希望这是好事。\n\n我们应该可以从残骸中回收一些资源。"
ADD colony.2020.a.tooltip:1 "Adds the following to the surface of [Root.GetName]:\n£energy£ §G+3§!\n\n"
CN2 colony.2020.a.tooltip:1 " [Root.GetName] 的地表增加下列资源：\n£energy §G+3§!"
ADD colony.2020.b.tooltip:1 "Adds the following to the surface of [Root.GetName]:\n£minerals£ §G+3§!\n\n"
CN2 colony.2020.b.tooltip:1 " [Root.GetName] 的地表增加下列资源：\n£minerals §G+3§!"
ADD colony.2025.name:0 "What Separates Us"
CN2 colony.2025.name:0 "种群隔阂"
ADD colony.2025.desc:0 "Having other species living with our people has caused some friction on [Root.GetName]. Be it cultural differences, xenophobia or a common misunderstanding is hard to tell, but what is sure is that these small encounters could turn to the worse if we do not intervene."
CN2 colony.2025.desc:0 "在 [Root.GetName] 上，我们的种群和混居的其他种群产生了不和。具体原因未知，可能是因为文化区别、自我封闭或者单单的误解。但很明显，若是放任不管，这些小型冲突就会愈演愈烈。"
ADD colony.2025.phobe.desc:0 "The xenos living among us have begun to cause friction on [Root.GetName]. Our own people are furious, resulting in more and more fights breaking out each day. If we idly stand by the xenos might end up losing more than some bodily fluids."
CN2 colony.2025.phobe.desc:0 "在 [Root.GetName] 上，混居在我们其中的异星人开始惹是生非了。这引起了我们民众的众怒，每天都有越来越多的争斗彰显。如果坐视不理，那些异星人估计会损失惨重。"
ADD colony.2025.phile.desc:0 "Having our own species living together with other lifeforms isn't always easy. Some friction has begun to take form on [Root.GetName], surely due to our inability to incorporate the aliens into our society properly. If nothing is done they might be at risk."
CN2 colony.2025.phile.desc:0 "与其他种群共生并非易事。在 [Root.GetName] 星上，由于无法让外星人合理融入我方社会，一些不和悄然形成。如果仍然不采取行动，或许会产生危机。"
ADD colony.2025.a:0 "Distract the angry mob."
CN2 colony.2025.a:0 "分散狂躁大众。"
