ADD colony.2030.name:0 "Colonial Assassin"
CN2 colony.2030.name:0 "殖民刺客"
ADD colony.2030.desc.base:0 "Our governor on §Y[Root.GetName]§! has been found dead! The perpetrator was caught trying to make an escape, an assassin sent by the §Y[AssassinEmpire.GetName]§!."
CN2 colony.2030.desc.base:0 "我们发现在§Y [Root.GetName] §!的总督已经死亡！有人目击了试图逃跑的犯人，刺客来自§Y [AssassinEmpire.GetName] §!。"
ADD colony.2030.desc:0 "$colony.2030.desc.base$ What we do with the perpetrator is sure to cause ripples on our already unstable relationship."
CN2 colony.2030.desc:0 "$colony.2030.desc.base$我们对犯人的处置会对我们本已紧张的关系造成影响。"
ADD colony.2030.desc.military:0 "$colony.2030.desc.base$ This disrespectful act of aggression can only be the beginning."
CN2 colony.2030.desc.military:0 "$colony.2030.desc.base$这种充满挑战的来犯行为仅仅只是一个开始。"
ADD colony.2030.desc.phobe:0 "$colony.2030.desc.base$ The xenos' disrespect knows no bounds."
CN2 colony.2030.desc.phobe:0 "$colony.2030.desc.base$外星人不会懂得收敛。"
ADD colony.2030.desc.spirit:0 "$colony.2030.desc.base$ This attack is not only an attack on our people, but an attack on the divine itself."
CN2 colony.2030.desc.spirit:0 "$colony.2030.desc.base$这次攻击不仅仅只是针对我们，更是针对我们的神灵。"
ADD colony.2030.a:0 "Send the assassin home safely to show good faith."
CN2 colony.2030.a:0 "将刺客安全遣返以示诚意。"
ADD colony.2030.a.tooltip:0 "The §Y[AssassinEmpire.GetName]§! gains the §G$assassination_forgiven$§! opinion modifier towards the §Y[MyCountry.GetName]§!:\n£opinion£ Opinion §G+35§!\n"
CN2 colony.2030.a.tooltip:0 "§Y [AssassinEmpire.GetName] §!获得对§Y [MyCountry.GetName] §!的§G$assassination_forgiven$§!评价修正：\n£opinion评价§G+35§!"
ADD colony.2030.b:0 "Keep the assassin as an information source."
CN2 colony.2030.b:0 "从刺客口中套出更多信息。"
ADD colony.2030.c:0 "Execute the assassin to send a message."
CN2 colony.2030.c:0 "消灭刺客并传递消息。"
ADD colony.2030.d:0 "Execute the assassin to display our superiority."
CN2 colony.2030.d:0 "消灭刺客以显示力量。"
ADD colony.2035.name:0 "Infectious"
CN2 colony.2035.name:0 "传染性"
ADD colony.2035.desc:0 "Several population districts on [Root.GetName] are reporting people falling ill, on an unprecedented scale. Anyone affected by one of this disease's many strains can barely move and are succumbed to vile extrusions.\n\nIf left uncontrolled this sickness might be the end of [Root.GetName]."
CN2 colony.2035.desc:0 " [Root.GetName] 的部分人口聚集区报告表示，民众遭受了史无前例的大规模传染病。这种疾病有多株病原体。被感染的患者几乎无法行动并产生严重呼吸困难。\n\n若疫情不加以控制， [Root.GetName] 将迎来末日。"
ADD colony.2035.desc.material:0 "Several population districts on [Root.GetName] have filed reports of civilians falling ill to a vicious sickness. It spreads quickly, it has multiple, fast evolving strains, and could halt production and expansion if not taken care of.\n\nIf not acted upon fast the colony might fall, setting us back years in development."
CN2 colony.2035.desc.material:0 " [Root.GetName] 的一些人口聚集区提交报告表示，该地民众受到了某种严重疾病感染。该疾病传播极为迅速，并有许多不断迅速演化的病原体，如不及时介入将阻碍地区生产及发展。\n\n如不迅速采取措施，殖民地建设将停滞甚至倒退数年。"
ADD colony.2035.desc.spirit:0 "Several population districts on [Root.GetName] have fallen ill to an ungodly new disease, unknown to our scientists. The vile sickness evolves, making it hard to understand, but all types of it makes the mind falter as it festers in the body.\n\nIf no measures are taken we might lose many a soul to the darkness."
CN2 colony.2035.desc.spirit:0 " [Root.GetName] 的一些人口聚集区陷入了某种未知且极为可怕的疫情。科学家对此一无所知。由于并发症多样，该疾病一时让人束手无策。而这些并发症最终都会随病毒扩散全身而导致患者神志不清。\n\n如不采取措施，许多无辜灵魂将堕入黑暗。"
ADD colony.2035.a:0 "Build a hospital we can send the ill to for study."
CN2 colony.2035.a:0 "建造医院以安置患者并加以研究。"
ADD colony.2035.a.tooltip:0 "Places a £building£ §Y$building_quarantine$§! on §Y[Root.GetName]§!.\n\n"
CN2 colony.2035.a.tooltip:0 "将一栋£building §Y$building_quarantine$§!放置于§Y [Root.GetName] §!。"
ADD colony.2035.b.tooltip:0 "§RReplaces 1§! existing building on §Y[Root.GetName]§! with a £building£ §Y$building_quarantine$§!.\n\n"
CN2 colony.2035.b.tooltip:0 "将一栋§Y [Root.GetName] §!的现存建筑§R替换§!为一栋£building §Y$building_quarantine$§!。"
ADD colony.2035.c:0 "Force the infected into quarantine."
CN2 colony.2035.c:0 "命令感染者进入隔离区。"
ADD colony.2035.c.spirit:0 "Isolate the tainted souls and pray it is enough."
CN2 colony.2035.c.spirit:0 "将感染者隔离并为他们祈祷便已足够。"
ADD colony.2035.c.tooltip:0 "Removes the infected Pops on §Y[Root.GetName]§!.\n\n"
CN2 colony.2035.c.tooltip:0 "将§Y [Root.GetName] §!的感染成员全部清除。"
ADD colony.2035.c.material:0 "Euthanize the infected, remove the risk of spreading."
CN2 colony.2035.c.material:0 "让受感染成员没有痛苦地消失，杜绝传播风险。"
ADD colony.2035.c.badguy:0 "Execute the infected population."
CN2 colony.2035.c.badguy:0 "将感染者全部消灭。"
ADD colony.2035.c.tooltip.kill:0 "Kills the infected Pops on [Root.GetName].\n\n"
CN2 colony.2035.c.tooltip.kill:0 "消灭掉 [Root.GetName] 的全部感染成员。"
ADD colony.2036.desc:0 "Even though we tried to limit the risk of spreading, the disease on [Root.GetName] seems more difficult to get rid of than we first thought. More individuals have emerged with the same symptoms. We might have to rethink how we approach this issue."
CN2 colony.2036.desc:0 "即便我们竭力试图控制传播风险， [Root.GetName] 的疾病看上去比我们预估的更加难以处理。更多人产生了相同病症。我们必须重新思考解决方案。"
ADD colony.2036.c:0 "Force the infected into quarantine again."
CN2 colony.2036.c:0 "强制感染者再次进入隔离区。"
ADD colony.2036.c.spirit:0 "Isolate the newly tainted souls."
CN2 colony.2036.c.spirit:0 "将新的感染者进行隔离。"
ADD colony.2036.c.material:0 "Euthanize the infected again."
CN2 colony.2036.c.material:0 "再次让感染者没有痛苦地消失。"
ADD colony.2036.c.badguy:0 "Execute the infected population again."
CN2 colony.2036.c.badguy:0 "再次将感染者全部消灭。"
ADD colony.2040.desc:0 "[Root.GetName] is quickly being overrun by the disease. We need to act fast and send a population to the emergency research station. Hopefully we can find a cure, if they survive until we find the root cause."
CN2 colony.2040.desc:0 "疾病迅速在 [Root.GetName] 上泛滥成灾。我们需要迅速行动并将感染者送入紧急研究所。希望我们可以找到治疗方案，如果他们能撑到我们找到发病根源的话。"
ADD colony.2046.desc:0 "The disease ravaging [Root.GetName] has claimed its first victim. We need to make sure the emergency clinic has a test group to study, in order to increase the likelihood of finding a cure."
CN2 colony.2046.desc:0 "肆虐 [Root.GetName] 的疾病已经带走了第一名受害者。我们需要确保急救站中有试验小组对疾病进行研究，从而增加找到治疗方案的可能性。"
ADD colony.2046.a:0 "Give me updates if any more die."
CN2 colony.2046.a:0 "如果有更多人死亡，及时告知我。"
ADD colony.2046.b:0 "Don't update me."
CN2 colony.2046.b:0 "不要告知我最新情况。"
ADD colony.2047.desc:0 "Another group of infected falls dead on [Root.GetName] from the disease."
CN2 colony.2047.desc:0 " [Root.GetName] 的又一批感染者逝世了。"
ADD colony.2041.desc:1 "The emergency clinic on [Root.GetName] seems to have been able to cure its test group from their illness. We should send more there for treatment."
CN2 colony.2041.desc:1 " [Root.GetName] 的一座急救站在临床试验中成功治愈了一批病患。我们应该派更多病人过去接受治疗。"
ADD colony.2041.b.desc:0 "The clinic on [Root.GetName] has collected random samples from the populace and been able to cure one group's strand of the disease. We should send people to the clinic for faster treatment."
CN2 colony.2041.b.desc:0 " [Root.GetName] 的一家诊所对患者进行了随机采样分组，并成功治愈了其中一组患者的疾病。我们应当派人们前去诊所以加速确认治疗方案。"
ADD colony.2042.desc:0 "After managing to cure various strands of the illness on [Root.GetName] our research staff has been able to synthesize a vaccine. With this we can quickly cure the entire population and the horror is finally over!"
CN2 colony.2042.desc:0 "在成功治疗 [Root.GetName] 的多名患者之后，我们的研究人员成功合成出疫苗。有了疫苗以后我们就能够迅速治愈全部患者。疫情带来的恐慌终于迎来终结！"
ADD colony.2043.desc:0 "The last of the infected on [Root.GetName] is no more. It appears that the disease cannot spread to any new hosts at this point."
CN2 colony.2043.desc:0 " [Root.GetName] 的最后一名感染者成功被治愈。看上去疾病在此时已经找不到新的宿主了。"
ADD colony.2044.desc:0 "[Root.GetName] stands empty. The [Root.GetPlanetMoon]'s population has been totally wiped out. The good news is that this must have eradicated even the disease and we should be able to repopulate."
CN2 colony.2044.desc:0 " [Root.GetName] 成为了一颗死星。 [Root.GetPlanetMoon] 的人口已经被全部清除。好消息是让人束手无策的疾病也被清除了。我们现在可以重新发展。"
ADD colony.2043.a:0 "The scourge is over."
CN2 colony.2043.a:0 "灾祸终结了。"
ADD colony.2050.name:0 "Lost to Bureaucracy"
CN2 colony.2050.name:0 "官员失败"
ADD colony.2050.desc:0 "Due to a major clerical error parts of [Root.GetName] has fallen behind in infrastructure maintenance and accommodation services. The people live in rather bleak conditions and will not tolerate it for long. Remedying these problems will cost us time and effort."
CN2 colony.2050.desc:0 "由于重大的记录错误， [Root.GetName] 部分区域的基础设施维护与住宅服务已趋于落后。人们正居住在较为恶劣的环境之中，似乎已忍不了太久了。要修复这些问题则会耗费我们的时间与精力。"
ADD colony.2050.a.tooltip:1 "[Root.GetName] gains the following:\n$decrepit_dwellings$ §R+1§!\n$failing_infrastructure$ §R+1§!"
CN2 colony.2050.a.tooltip:1 " [Root.GetName] 获得以下结果：\n$decrepit_dwellings$§R+1§!\n$failing_infrastructure$§R+1§!"
ADD colony.2050.b:0 "We must invest in this area."
CN2 colony.2050.b:0 "我们必须对此区域进行投资。"
ADD colony.2050.c:0 "We have a strong community, help them recover."
CN2 colony.2050.c:0 "我们有强大的团队，帮助他们复原。"
ADD colony.2050.d:0 "Throw out the inhabitants and raze the area."
CN2 colony.2050.d:0 "驱逐该地居民并将该片区域夷为平地。"
ADD colony.2050.d.tooltip:0 "§S2 £building£ Buildings§! on §Y[Root.GetName]§! are §Rruined§!.\n\n§B2 £pops£ Pops§! on §Y[Root.GetName]§! gain the §R$pop_angered$§! modifier for §Y24§! months, with the following effects:\nResource Output §R-25%§!\n£happiness£ Happiness §R-25%§!\n\n"
CN2 colony.2050.d.tooltip:0 "§Y [Root.GetName] §!上的§S2栋£building建筑§!已被§R毁毁§!。\n\n§Y [Root.GetName] §!上的§B2个£pops人口§!获得§R$pop_angered$§!修正，持续§Y24§!个月，效果如下：\n资源产出§R-25%§!\n£happiness幸福度§R-25%§!"
